&#160; 

In 2021, Devon completed the sale of non-core assets in the Rockies for proceeds of $ 9 million, net of purchase price adjustments, and recognized a $ 35 million gain related to the sale. Devon received $ 4 million in contingent earnout payments related to this transaction in the first quarters of 2023 and 2022. The total estimated proved reserves associated with these divested assets was approximately 3 MMBoe.&#8204; 

