Equity &#8211; Devon&#8217;s equity securities include commingled global equity funds that invest in large, mid and small capitalization stocks across the world&#8217;s developed and emerging markets and international large cap equity securities. These equity securities can be sold on demand but are not actively traded. The fair values of these securities are based upon the net asset values provided by the investment managers and were $ 49 million and $ 67 million at December 31, 2022 and 2021, respectively. 

